@{
    ViewBag.Title = "About Us - Book Reader";
}

<section class="about-page">
    <div class="container">
        <h1>About Book Reader</h1>
        <div class="about-content">
            <div class="about-intro">
                <h2>Platform Overview</h2>
                <p>Book Reader is a platform dedicated to providing high-quality e-book reading services, committed to creating a convenient and comfortable reading experience for users. We have gathered premium books across multiple fields including programming, science fiction, literature, history, and art, covering full-range content from beginner to advanced levels.</p>
                <p>Since its launch in 2023, the platform has included more than 1,000 genuine e-books and served over 100,000 users cumulatively, becoming the preferred reading platform for numerous readers and learners.</p>
            </div>

            <div class="about-mission">
                <h2>Our Mission</h2>
                <p>To make reading accessible to all and democratize knowledge for the public. We firmly believe that high-quality reading resources should be available to more people, so we always adhere to the philosophy of "content is king, experience is paramount", continuously optimizing platform functions and enriching book categories.</p>
            </div>

            <div class="about-team">
                <h2>Our Team</h2>
                <p>Our team consists of senior book editors, technical developers, and user experience designers, with an average of over 5 years of industry experience, dedicated to providing professional and thoughtful reading services for users.</p>
            </div>

            <div class="about-values">
                <h2>Core Values</h2>
                <ul>
                    <li>✓ Integrity: Uphold genuine editions and respect copyrights</li>
                    <li>✓ Innovation: Continuously optimize product experience</li>
                    <li>✓ Service: Put user needs at the core</li>
                    <li>✓ Growth: Learn and progress together with users</li>
                </ul>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</section>